data.description: Why wait to build, when you can have it now! Move-in ready almost brand new built less than 6 months ago in Camp Creek Village. This exquisite 4-bedroom 2.5 bath home is ready for your family. Open concept chef's kitchen featuring a large island with white quartz and white cabinets, overlooking the family room. Upstairs is a loft area that's perfect for any family member to work or relax. The Primary bedroom is spacious with a huge walk-in closet, separate tub and shower. You have got to come see this beautiful home. Ask about our special financing program that has no downpayment no PMI.
